<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" itunes:timing="Word"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Hiding In The Blue"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="TheFatRat"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="RIELL"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Hiding In The Blue"/><amll:meta key="album" value="PARALLAX"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="1852002829"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="000D8ZDp4dmHAB"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="01qoJko9zf7xkwfYmrLwmk"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="4uhajAtJz72BBHkiIUvr7v"/><amll:meta key="appleMusicId" value="1758829562"/><amll:meta key="appleMusicId" value="1758835162"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="DEZC62102941"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="158539001"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="PhantomPixel-0418"/></metadata></head><body dur="03:19.275"><div begin="00:11.789" end="03:19.275"><p begin="00:11.789" end="00:15.040" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L1"><span begin="00:11.789" end="00:11.962">I'm</span> <span begin="00:11.962" end="00:12.382">alone</span> <span begin="00:12.382" end="00:12.561">here</span> <span begin="00:12.561" end="00:12.763">on</span> <span begin="00:12.763" end="00:13.201">my</span> <span begin="00:13.201" end="00:13.761">island,</span> <span begin="00:13.761" end="00:13.981">floating</span> <span begin="00:13.981" end="00:14.187">in</span> <span begin="00:14.187" end="00:14.567">the</span> <span begin="00:14.567" end="00:15.040">sky</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我独自在这座岛屿上，漂浮于天际</span></p><p begin="00:15.040" end="00:17.906" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L2"><span begin="00:15.040" end="00:15.357">I'm</span> <span begin="00:15.357" end="00:15.624">high</span> <span begin="00:15.624" end="00:16.045">above</span> <span begin="00:16.045" end="00:16.212">the</span> <span begin="00:16.212" end="00:16.398">world</span> <span begin="00:16.398" end="00:16.701">I</span> <span begin="00:16.701" end="00:17.166">used</span> <span begin="00:17.166" end="00:17.390">to</span> <span begin="00:17.390" end="00:17.906">know</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">高悬于我曾熟知的世界之上</span></p><p begin="00:18.158" end="00:21.513" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:18.158" end="00:18.345">And</span> <span begin="00:18.345" end="00:18.544">I'm</span> <span begin="00:18.544" end="00:18.686">far</span> <span begin="00:18.686" end="00:19.041">from</span> <span begin="00:19.041" end="00:19.308">any</span> <span begin="00:19.308" end="00:20.153">danger,</span> <span begin="00:20.153" end="00:20.354">safe</span> <span begin="00:20.354" end="00:20.565">from</span> <span begin="00:20.565" end="00:20.931">any</span> <span begin="00:20.931" end="00:21.513">failure</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">远离一切危险，躲过所有失败</span></p><p begin="00:21.735" end="00:24.302" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:21.735" end="00:21.962">Guarded,</span> <span begin="00:21.962" end="00:22.333">I</span> <span begin="00:22.333" end="00:22.557">found</span> <span begin="00:22.557" end="00:23.091">shelter</span> <span begin="00:23.091" end="00:23.550">in</span> <span begin="00:23.550" end="00:23.853">the</span> <span begin="00:23.853" end="00:24.302">storm</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">受庇护着，我在风暴中寻得栖身之所</span></p><p begin="00:24.747" end="00:28.772" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:24.747" end="00:24.891">I'm</span> <span begin="00:24.891" end="00:25.274">hiding</span> <span begin="00:25.274" end="00:25.490">in</span> <span begin="00:25.490" end="00:25.662">the</span> <span begin="00:25.662" end="00:28.772">blue</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我藏匿于蔚蓝之中</span></p><p begin="00:28.772" end="00:31.280" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:28.772" end="00:29.306">Safe</span> <span begin="00:29.306" end="00:30.081">between</span> <span begin="00:30.081" end="00:30.376">the</span> <span begin="00:30.376" end="00:31.280">clouds</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">安睡在云层之间</span></p><p begin="00:31.280" end="00:37.223" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:31.280" end="00:31.689">In</span> <span begin="00:31.689" end="00:32.088">the</span> <span begin="00:32.088" end="00:35.201">blue</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="00:35.274" end="00:37.223"><span begin="00:35.274" end="00:35.670">(Where</span> <span begin="00:35.670" end="00:36.022">I</span> <span begin="00:36.022" end="00:36.475">can't</span> <span begin="00:36.475" end="00:36.716">be</span> <span begin="00:36.716" end="00:37.223">found)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">无人能够找到我</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在那片蓝里</span></p><p begin="00:37.348" end="00:40.853" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:37.348" end="00:37.480">Was</span> <span begin="00:37.480" end="00:37.611">a</span> <span begin="00:37.611" end="00:38.110">soldier</span> <span begin="00:38.110" end="00:38.281">in</span> <span begin="00:38.281" end="00:38.557">the</span> <span begin="00:38.557" end="00:39.292">legions,</span> <span begin="00:39.292" end="00:39.655">fought</span> <span begin="00:39.655" end="00:39.892">against</span> <span begin="00:39.892" end="00:40.075">the</span> <span begin="00:40.075" end="00:40.853">demons</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我曾是军团中的一员，与恶魔搏斗</span></p><p begin="00:40.898" end="00:43.698" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:40.898" end="00:41.120">Fought</span> <span begin="00:41.120" end="00:41.478">against</span> <span begin="00:41.478" end="00:41.695">the</span> <span begin="00:41.695" end="00:42.330">monsters</span> <span begin="00:42.330" end="00:42.690">made</span> <span begin="00:42.690" end="00:43.081">of</span> <span begin="00:43.081" end="00:43.698">gold</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">对抗那些由黄金铸就的怪物</span></p><p begin="00:43.698" end="00:47.292" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:43.698" end="00:43.888">But</span> <span begin="00:43.888" end="00:44.085">they</span> <span begin="00:44.085" end="00:44.473">stormed</span> <span begin="00:44.473" end="00:44.753">across</span> <span begin="00:44.753" end="00:45.688">Arcadia,</span> <span begin="00:45.688" end="00:46.260">following</span> <span begin="00:46.260" end="00:46.480">their</span> <span begin="00:46.480" end="00:47.292">nature</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">可它们席卷了阿卡迪亚，依循本性</span></p><p begin="00:47.292" end="00:49.908" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="00:47.292" end="00:47.684">Washed</span> <span begin="00:47.684" end="00:47.891">away</span> <span begin="00:47.891" end="00:48.092">the</span> <span begin="00:48.092" end="00:48.388">place</span> <span begin="00:48.388" end="00:48.686">I</span> <span begin="00:48.686" end="00:49.137">once</span> <span begin="00:49.137" end="00:49.566">called</span> <span begin="00:49.566" end="00:49.908">home</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">冲垮了我曾称之为家的地方</span></p><p begin="00:50.337" end="00:54.417" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="00:50.337" end="00:50.477">I'm</span> <span begin="00:50.477" end="00:50.886">hiding</span> <span begin="00:50.886" end="00:51.127">in</span> <span begin="00:51.127" end="00:51.373">the</span> <span begin="00:51.373" end="00:54.417">blue</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我藏匿于蔚蓝之中</span></p><p begin="00:54.417" end="00:56.981" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="00:54.417" end="00:54.888">Safe</span> <span begin="00:54.888" end="00:55.671">between</span> <span begin="00:55.671" end="00:55.982">the</span> <span begin="00:55.982" end="00:56.981">clouds</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">安睡在云层之间</span></p><p begin="00:56.959" end="01:00.869" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="00:56.959" end="00:57.591">In</span> <span begin="00:57.591" end="00:57.961">the</span> <span begin="00:57.961" end="01:00.869">blue</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在那片蓝里</span></p><p begin="01:00.869" end="01:03.109" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="01:00.869" end="01:01.319">Where</span> <span begin="01:01.319" end="01:01.777">I</span> <span begin="01:01.777" end="01:02.182">can't</span> <span begin="01:02.182" end="01:02.542">be</span> <span begin="01:02.542" end="01:03.109">found</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">无人能够找到我</span></p><p begin="01:03.125" end="01:04.123" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="01:03.125" end="01:03.363">I'm</span> <span begin="01:03.363" end="01:03.702">hiding</span> <span begin="01:03.702" end="01:03.772">in</span> <span begin="01:03.772" end="01:03.990">the</span> <span begin="01:03.990" end="01:04.123">blue</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我藏匿于蔚蓝之中</span></p><p begin="01:15.949" end="01:17.422" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="01:15.949" end="01:16.188">I'm</span> <span begin="01:16.188" end="01:16.546">hiding</span> <span begin="01:16.546" end="01:16.736">in</span> <span begin="01:16.736" end="01:16.943">the</span> <span begin="01:16.943" end="01:17.422">blue</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我藏匿于蔚蓝之中</span></p><p begin="01:28.732" end="01:32.118" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="01:28.732" end="01:28.944">As</span> <span begin="01:28.944" end="01:29.162">time</span> <span begin="01:29.162" end="01:29.338">goes</span> <span begin="01:29.338" end="01:29.758">racing</span> <span begin="01:29.758" end="01:30.164">by,</span> <span begin="01:30.164" end="01:30.609">I'm</span> <span begin="01:30.609" end="01:30.945">wishing</span> <span begin="01:30.945" end="01:31.146">I</span> <span begin="01:31.146" end="01:31.337">could</span> <span begin="01:31.337" end="01:31.614">be</span> <span begin="01:31.614" end="01:32.118">fine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">时光飞驰，我多希望可以释怀</span></p><p begin="01:32.170" end="01:34.728" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="01:32.170" end="01:32.348">But</span> <span begin="01:32.348" end="01:32.480">I'm</span> <span begin="01:32.480" end="01:32.681">still</span> <span begin="01:32.681" end="01:32.928">so</span> <span begin="01:32.928" end="01:33.212">stuck</span> <span begin="01:33.212" end="01:33.562">on</span> <span begin="01:33.562" end="01:33.747">what</span> <span begin="01:33.747" end="01:34.028">used</span> <span begin="01:34.028" end="01:34.383">to</span> <span begin="01:34.383" end="01:34.728">be</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">却仍困在过往的影子里</span></p><p begin="01:34.948" end="01:38.381" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="01:34.948" end="01:35.126">Made</span> <span begin="01:35.126" end="01:35.276">a</span> <span begin="01:35.276" end="01:35.777">prison</span> <span begin="01:35.777" end="01:35.998">out</span> <span begin="01:35.998" end="01:36.190">of</span> <span begin="01:36.190" end="01:36.452">my</span> <span begin="01:36.452" end="01:36.945">mind,</span> <span begin="01:36.945" end="01:37.167">watch</span> <span begin="01:37.167" end="01:37.356">life</span> <span begin="01:37.356" end="01:37.561">as</span> <span begin="01:37.561" end="01:37.748">it</span> <span begin="01:37.748" end="01:38.156">goes</span> <span begin="01:38.156" end="01:38.381">by</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">将心囚禁成牢笼，静看生命流逝</span></p><p begin="01:38.539" end="01:41.149" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="01:38.539" end="01:38.919">Battle-</span><span begin="01:38.919" end="01:39.168">scarred,</span> <span begin="01:39.168" end="01:39.341">my</span> <span begin="01:39.341" end="01:39.714">own</span> <span begin="01:39.714" end="01:39.954">worst</span> <span begin="01:39.954" end="01:41.149">enemy</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">伤痕累累，却最怕面对自己</span></p><p begin="01:41.569" end="01:45.564" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="01:41.569" end="01:41.751">I'm</span> <span begin="01:41.751" end="01:42.125">hiding</span> <span begin="01:42.125" end="01:42.372">in</span> <span begin="01:42.372" end="01:42.578">the</span> <span begin="01:42.578" end="01:45.564">blue</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我藏匿于蔚蓝之中</span></p><p begin="01:45.589" end="01:47.768" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L23"><span begin="01:45.589" end="01:46.129">Safe</span> <span begin="01:46.129" end="01:46.889">between</span> <span begin="01:46.889" end="01:47.319">the</span> <span begin="01:47.319" end="01:47.768">clouds</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">安睡在云层之间</span></p><p begin="01:48.099" end="01:51.810" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L24"><span begin="01:48.099" end="01:48.343">In</span> <span begin="01:48.343" end="01:48.829">the</span> <span begin="01:48.829" end="01:51.810">blue</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在那片蓝里</span></p><p begin="01:51.995" end="01:54.148" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L25"><span begin="01:51.995" end="01:52.456">Where</span> <span begin="01:52.456" end="01:52.845">I</span> <span begin="01:52.845" end="01:53.302">can't</span> <span begin="01:53.302" end="01:53.536">be</span> <span begin="01:53.536" end="01:54.148">found</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">无人能够找到我</span></p><p begin="01:54.272" end="01:55.912" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L26"><span begin="01:54.272" end="01:54.494">I'm</span> <span begin="01:54.494" end="01:54.900">hiding</span> <span begin="01:54.900" end="01:55.076">in</span> <span begin="01:55.076" end="01:55.277">the</span> <span begin="01:55.277" end="01:55.912">blue</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我藏匿于蔚蓝之中</span></p><p begin="02:07.144" end="02:08.831" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L27"><span begin="02:07.144" end="02:07.353">I'm</span> <span begin="02:07.353" end="02:07.747">hiding</span> <span begin="02:07.747" end="02:07.929">in</span> <span begin="02:07.929" end="02:08.151">the</span> <span begin="02:08.151" end="02:08.831">blue</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我藏匿于蔚蓝之中</span></p><p begin="02:13.680" end="02:19.621" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L28"><span begin="02:13.680" end="02:14.082">Hiding</span> <span begin="02:14.082" end="02:14.288">in</span> <span begin="02:14.288" end="02:14.484">the</span> <span begin="02:14.484" end="02:19.621">blue</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">藏匿于蔚蓝</span></p><p begin="02:21.671" end="02:26.807" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L29"><span begin="02:21.671" end="02:21.911">The</span> <span begin="02:21.911" end="02:22.515">world's</span> <span begin="02:22.515" end="02:23.090">passing</span> <span begin="02:23.090" end="02:23.694">by,</span> <span begin="02:23.694" end="02:24.139">and</span> <span begin="02:24.887" end="02:25.273">I</span> <span begin="02:25.273" end="02:25.679">lost</span> <span begin="02:25.679" end="02:25.936">sense</span> <span begin="02:25.936" end="02:26.233">of</span> <span begin="02:26.233" end="02:26.807">time</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">世界匆匆掠过，我已失却时间感</span></p><p begin="02:26.935" end="02:33.371" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L30"><span begin="02:26.935" end="02:27.194">I've</span> <span begin="02:27.767" end="02:27.992">gone</span> <span begin="02:27.992" end="02:28.793">numb,</span> <span begin="02:28.793" end="02:28.950">I</span> <span begin="02:28.950" end="02:29.216">miss</span> <span begin="02:29.216" end="02:29.574">the</span> <span begin="02:29.574" end="02:30.192">days</span> <span begin="02:30.192" end="02:30.534">when</span> <span begin="02:31.281" end="02:31.639">we</span> <span begin="02:31.639" end="02:31.918">were</span> <span begin="02:31.918" end="02:32.741">making</span> <span begin="02:32.741" end="02:33.371">legends</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">麻木着，怀念那些我们共同缔造传奇的日子</span></p><p begin="02:3